channel.title: Need Help With Using A Diff Client And Source
channel.description:
I have a client from somewhere, and a source from a different place...

item.title: Need Help With Using A Diff Client And Source
item.dc:creator: @Wintercanon Wintercanon
item.description:
@Wintercanon wrote:

[quote=“ReDDD, post:2, topic:386888”]you cant, try get a client and source that come togeather :)[/quote]Why? It is just an older revision of the Runescape client.

Use a source or framework that wasn’t built of winterLove’s botting test server. Actually use a source that was built to be a Runescape emulator.
